{"tid":2337664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工人7.1衝警防線原判監6周改囚9個月 彭偉昌:任何與反修例有關的非法集結都有極高風險 刑責不能低估","createTime":"2020-12-23T12:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T17:47:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1b7d30ff1d902c3a596d89aaaee2135b50e6aa","tid":2337664,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/12/%E6%BD%98%E5%85%86%E5%88%9D-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E5%BA%AD-%E5%BD%AD%E5%81%89%E6%98%8C-20201203224950_14cc_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F12%2F%25E6%25BD%2598%25E5%2585%2586%25E5%2588%259D-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%25BA%25AD-%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%2581%2589%25E6%2598%258C-20201203224950_14cc_large.jpg&h=efa9a83e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n審理本案的三名法官：潘兆初、彭偉昌及潘敏琦<br />\n<br />\n地盤工人於去年七一回歸紀念日，在金鐘政府總部外集結。他承認非法集結罪，原被判監6星期，律政司則提出刑期覆核。<strong>上訴庭早前在地盤工已離港的情況下，改判監禁9個月，並發出拘捕令。</strong>而上訴庭今(23日)頒發判辭解釋理據，指當時反修例的浪潮正如火如荼，任何相關的非法集結都有極高的風險。 而地盤工不但喊出極具挑釁性的咒罵，還與其他人合力拉動路障衝擊警方，其個人行為對其他示威者有挑動作用，其罪責不能被低估，故需加重刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n36歲被告被控於去年7月1日在金鐘夏愨道與演藝道交界，與其他身份不詳的人參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭法官彭偉昌在判辭指，案發日是2019年的回歸紀念日，反對《逃犯條例》修訂的浪潮正如火如荼，任何與此目的有關的非法集結都有極高的風險。<br />\n<br />\n法官又指，案發時於最前的過百名示威者，觀其衣飾裝備，明顯是有計劃而來，要衝擊警方，否則不會製作三角形的路障向警方防線步步進逼。示威者也一定知道，在他們背後的人群跟著他們推進。涉案時間不但長達30分鐘，到最後一次推進更可能因為雙方距離拉近，群眾會向警方投擲磚塊和鐵枝，案中沒有人受傷只是幸運。<br />\n<br />\n此外，本案被告的的裝備雖不及其他示威者齊全，但他選擇置身其中，喊叫極具挑釁性的咒罵，還與其他人合力拉動路障衝擊警方，罪責絕不能被低估，其個人行為對其他示威者也有挑動作用。故認為原審裁判官嚴重低估了本案的嚴重性，和被告的個人罪責。<br />\n<br />\n判案理由書:<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132564&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D132564%26currpage%3DT&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=358cf71d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=132564&amp;currpage=T</a>"},{"pid":"a9ed8912d00f8facd8f05df26f7821fc55d6bc39","tid":2337664,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/zEEQ8Gr.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzEEQ8Gr.jpg&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=10db3470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/zEEQ8Gr.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"bef2203941e1dffabc8d935c8fe194a01fa92823","tid":2337664,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a6ecae8a6e14d52c19af950183e675b926164a","tid":2337664,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07898da374f09d276d7847309ce451d259481a75","tid":2337664,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64c943467aea97cca6626528ec0f08654cf15e3","tid":2337664,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9ed8912d00f8facd8f05df26f7821fc55d6bc39","tid":2337664,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/zEEQ8Gr.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzEEQ8Gr.jpg&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=10db3470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/zEEQ8Gr.jpg</a>"},"citedBy